{"title":"党的好女儿","authors":["吴鑫"],"dates":[{"year":1979,"month":6,"day":30}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"党的好女儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京机电设备公司  吴鑫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"信 仰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任凭屠刀寒光闪闪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任凭子弹穿透胸膛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宁死不屈的张志新啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"始终坚定着崇高信仰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这信仰曾经在烈火中诞生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这信仰也使你在斗争中成长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向往着共产主义，向往着赤旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞扬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从小，就把爱憎倾注琴弦上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愤火使你成为强者，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱的花朵终将自由地开放。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刽子手决不能逍遥法外，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也休想动摇我们心中的信仰！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"墓碑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史就在这里思索："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回龙岗上立起了你高高的墓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碑——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么光明正大反受诬陷？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么坚持真理却判了个死"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"罪？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史就在这里前进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回龙岗上立起了你的墓碑——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是真正的栋梁呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顶天立地，风雨难摧！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}